name: cOFFee
description:
Title: cOFFee
Location: Silverton, Oregon
Year Taken: 2004
About this photo: I didn’t spend much time in Silverton photographing for my own pleasure, and I think I’m going to go back to capture the town more often. It’s a beautiful, historic downtown with local restaurants, a fun park, and it’s just relaxing to hang out there. This particular photo came from a local coffee shop that had closed for the evening. In other words, the owner and employees were ‘Off’.
